{"arkId":"cl010111813","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010111813","modified ":"2026-03-11","title":"Manteau d\u0027officier de l\u0027Ordre du Saint-Esprit","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Manteau d\u0027officier de l\u0027Ordre du Saint-Esprit"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Philippe d\u0027Orl\u00e9ans (1715-1723) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons) ; Louis XV (1715-1774) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : vers 1722 (ancienne datation XVIIe si\u00e8cle)","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1722,"endYear":"","imprecision":"vers","text":"1er quart du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Anonyme","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Brodeur","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q4233718"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"MS 53","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"},{"value":"CL 18558","type":"Autre num\u00e9ro d\u0027inventaire"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"textile divers ; manteau de c\u00e9r\u00e9monie","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Manteau d\u0027officier de l\u0027ordre du Saint-Esprit en velours de soie noir, brod\u00e9 d\u0027un semis de 478 flammes d\u0027or et d\u0027argent sur toute la surface. La partie sup\u00e9rieure est recouverte d\u0027un mantelet en toile d\u0027argent verte, brod\u00e9e des m\u00eames motifs.Une plaque d\u0027argent repr\u00e9sentant une colombe est brod\u00e9e sur la face du manteau. \r\nLe manteau des quatre officiers qui administraient l\u0027Ordre (pr\u00e9v\u00f4t ma\u00eetre des c\u00e9r\u00e9monies, grand tr\u00e9sorier, greffier-secr\u00e9taire, h\u00e9raut) \u00e9tait semblable \u00e0 celui des chevaliers mais n\u0027\u00e9tait pas brod\u00e9 du motif du collier de l\u0027ordre sur sa bordure.\r\nL\u0027ensemble \u00e9tait doubl\u00e9 de satin jaune orang\u00e9.\r\nLe manteau est de forme ovo\u00efdale avec un effet de tra\u00eene. Il est compos\u00e9 de huit l\u00e9s de velours de soie d\u0027une largeur de 52,5 cm de couture \u00e0 couture chacun et d\u0027un l\u00e9 de 22 cm pour la tra\u00eene .\r\nLa fente d\u0027ouverture est \u00e0 droite, le manteau pouvant se retrousser \u00e0 gauche.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"159","displayDimension":"159 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Longueur","value":"420","displayDimension":"420 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"290","displayDimension":"290 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":5,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau\/Technique : Velours de soie noir brod\u00e9 de fils d\u0027or et d\u0027argent (pour le manteau)\r\nTechnique : velours (techniques textile-\u003Etissu uni)\r\nTechnique : broderie en guipure (techniques textile-\u003Ebroderie)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : soie (velours et doublure)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : argent (fils, lames, et plaques)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : or (fils et lames d\u0027argent dor\u00e9)","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Trianon ; Mus\u00e9e des Souverains","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Re